m/threats-violence-and-racist-remarks-israel-sees-surge-of-hostility-against-arab-workers/0000018b-6c07-d326-a39b-6e1f9be30000</guid></item><item><title>“在加沙周围遭受酷刑和游行：”被绑架的以色列-德国狂欢者确认死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/tortured-and-paraded-around-gaza-abducted-israeli-german-raver-confirmed-dead/0000018b-8001-d1da-a1bb-edb9c2330000</link><description>两周前，德国媒体报道称，拥有德国和以色列双重国籍的 23 岁沙尼·洛克 (Shani Louk) 在加沙地带北部的一家医院病重，随后被证实死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/tortured-and-paraded-around-gaza-abducted-israeli-german-raver-confirmed-dead/0000018b-8001-d1da-a1bb-edb9c2330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报部建议哈马斯战争后将加沙人迁往西奈半岛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-document-suggests-possible-relocation-of-gazans-to-northern-sinai/0000018b-7ff6-d1da-a1bb-7ffe83ed0000</link><description>以色列情报部准备的一份文件草案提出了一种选择，即首先将加沙人口迁移到西奈半岛北部的帐篷城。这是政治领导层可能采取退出战争战略的第一个迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 10:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-document-suggests-possible-relocation-of-gazans-to-northern-sinai/0000018b-7ff6-d1da-a1bb-7ffe83ed0000</guid></item><item><title>反犹太骚乱后警方控制俄罗斯达吉斯坦机场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/police-take-control-of-russias-dagestan-airport-after-antisemitic-riot/0000018b-7f8e-d51e-a3cb-7feeecb60000</link><description>该地区的骚乱令渴望维持国内稳定的俄罗斯总统普京头疼不已。达吉斯坦领导人谢尔盖·梅利科夫表示，这一事件严重违反了法律，尽管达吉斯坦人强调巴勒斯坦受害者的“痛苦”</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 09:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/police-take-control-of-russias-dagestan-airport-after-antisemitic-riot/0000018b-7f8e-d51e-a3cb-7feeecb60000</guid></item><item><title>包括美国在内的以色列各条战线的紧张局势都在酝酿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-the-south-north-and-with-the-u-s-israel-faces-an-escalation-on-all-fronts/0000018b-7d2e-d4a8-a3cf-fdaf26c90000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙的行动在保密的情况下扩大，政府希望增加的军事压力将推动被绑架者的谈判。 ■ 在约旦河西岸，定居者的暴力活动猖獗。以色列公众对内塔尼亚胡没有信心</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 05:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/in-the-south-north-and-with-the-u-s-israel-faces-an-escalation-on-all-fronts/0000018b-7d2e-d4a8-a3cf-fdaf26c90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的推文被党内同事视为“精神病”，可能会加速他的下台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tweet-could-hasten-his-ouster-party-colleagues-say/0000018b-7c8b-d51e-a3cb-7def36cb0000</link><description>以色列总理猛烈抨击军队和安全部门的决定进一步加剧了对他在利库德集团内部领导的批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 04:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tweet-could-hasten-his-ouster-party-colleagues-say/0000018b-7c8b-d51e-a3cb-7def36cb0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列坦克出现在加沙市郊区，军队加强地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-live/idf-attacks-in-syria-following-rocket-launches-antisemitic-riots-in-russian-airport/0000018b-7df0-d4a8-a3cf-fdf9c8530000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人证实，军队在加沙地带进行了“广泛”地面行动，部队与恐怖分子“直接交战” ■ 以色列警察在耶路撒冷发生疑似刺伤袭击后严重受伤 ■ 以色列国防军表示，过去 24 小时内，加沙约 600 个恐怖目标遭到袭击■ 周一上午，以色列国防军在约旦河西岸杰宁的行动中造成四名巴勒斯坦人死亡 ■ 以色列空军连夜袭击了叙利亚和黎巴嫩的目标 ■ 以色列国防军通知 239 名人质的家人，仍有 40 人失踪 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯至少有 1,300 人死亡 ■加沙卫生部：8,005名加沙人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Oct 2023 03:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-30/ty-article-live/idf-attacks-in-syria-following-rocket-launches-antisemitic-riots-in-russian-airport/0000018b-7df0-d4a8-a3cf-fdf9c8530000</guid></item><item><title>康奈尔希勒尔建议犹太学生和工作人员因受到威胁而避免去犹太餐厅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-30/ty-article/.premiu