our-month-detention-without-trial/0000018b-7cd8-d1da-a1bb-7df840580000</guid></item><item><title>来自以色列的航班降落后，人群涌入俄罗斯机场寻找犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/crowds-storm-russian-airport-as-flight-from-israel-lands/0000018b-7cbb-d51e-a3cb-7dff63d00000</link><description>马哈奇卡拉机场的镜头显示，愤怒的暴徒正在寻找飞机上的人，抗议者高呼反犹太口号，并“检查”离开该地的汽车。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 19:21:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/crowds-storm-russian-airport-as-flight-from-israel-lands/0000018b-7cbb-d51e-a3cb-7dff63d00000</guid></item><item><title>我通常对以色列小盘股持怀疑态度，但 Kfar Azza 的一只股票打破了我的愤世嫉俗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/im-usually-dubious-about-israeli-small-caps-but-one-from-kfar-azza-cracked-my-cynicism/0000018b-7c0f-d4a8-a3cf-fcaf2fdd0000</link><description>卡弗里特工业公司 (Kafrit Industries) 为塑料工业生产化合物，该公司的三名员工在战争中被杀。总部位于卡法阿扎，产品销往世界各地 - 可能会成为一项不错的投资</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 17:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/im-usually-dubious-about-israeli-small-caps-but-one-from-kfar-azza-cracked-my-cynicism/0000018b-7c0f-d4a8-a3cf-fcaf2fdd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质亲属致电内塔尼亚胡任命的协调员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-relatives-slam-call-with-coordinator-appointed-by-netanyahu/0000018b-7c31-d4a8-a3cf-fcb9b4f40000</link><description>被绑架到加沙的以色列人的家人表示，盖尔·赫希没有提供新信息，并建议他们接受国际媒体采访，以帮助确保亲人获释</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 17:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-relatives-slam-call-with-coordinator-appointed-by-netanyahu/0000018b-7c31-d4a8-a3cf-fcb9b4f40000</guid></item></channel></rss>